      <title>拉瓜迪亚机场航站楼改造后债务前景乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/laguardia-airport-debt-outlook-is-positive-after-terminal-revamp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级表示，拉瓜迪亚机场 B 航站楼耗资 40 亿美元进行改造近两年后，该航空枢纽的债务前景正在好转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/laguardia-airport-debt-outlook-is-positive-after-terminal-revamp</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 20:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
